Functions.question:
\[
  \forall X \subseteq \mathbb{R},\;
  \Bigl[
    \overline{X} = X
    \;\iff\;
    \forall (a_n)_{n=1}^\infty \subseteq X,\;
    \forall x \in \mathbb{R},\;
    \bigl(a_n \to x \;\Rightarrow\; x \in X\bigr)
  \Bigr].
\]

